1.过滤器(Filter)|拦截器(Interceptor)|处理器(Handler|Controller)执行顺序

    BaseFilter doFilter executed:/doWithFilterAndInterceptor
    ConcreteFilter doFilter executed:/doWithFilterAndInterceptor
    BaseInterceptor preHandle executed...
    ConcreteInterceptor preHandle executed...
    FilterAndInterceptorController executed...
    ConcreteInterceptor postHandle executed...
    BaseInterceptor postHandle executed...
    ConcreteInterceptor afterCompletion executed...
    BaseInterceptor afterCompletion executed...
    ConcreteFilter doFilter after:/doWithFilterAndInterceptor
    BaseFilter doFilter after:/doWithFilterAndInterceptor

2.Filter可以在
    public void doFilter(ServletRequest request, ServletResponse response,
                FilterChain chain) throws IOException, ServletException;
  方法中对request(调用具体的处理器之前)进行操作修改，也可以对response(调用具体的处理器之后)
  进行操作修改；

  Interceptor则不能，没办法对具体的处理器的request或response进行操作
    boolean preHandle(HttpServletRequest request, HttpServletResponse response, Object handler)
    			throws Exception;